race.description: Xxxx Gold Fillies And Mares Class 1 Handicap
race.comment: Robbed of the better chances after scratchings. That gives SEQUEL (9) the chance to keep the winning run going. Was midfield in a hot form race in heavy ground at Newcastle then shipped north and finally off the mark with her maiden here. Can measure up again. MEHRETU (1) was good fresh up here without a lot of luck and probably should have won. Got too far back latest and worth another chance. EVERY HEART (6) has been winding up strongly and can run on into the finish. SIRKEL (4) returns from a break on the back of a trial on the Sunshine Coast Inner Track. Opened last campaign with a third at Eagle Farm over 1200m. Resuming in easier and all best form is on rain affected going so capable of a bold return.
